x4freetext: Acquisition system : six ACQIRIS digitizers(420 x 106
maximum two inputs and a common trigger, which recorded
the waveforms from the HPGe preamplifiers and
transferred them to a PC for further processing.
Ti natural disk of 8.000+-0.001 cm diameter,
Gamma Array for Inelastic Neutron Scattering
with respect to the beam direction (4 at each angle)
at distances ~17 cm from the center of the sample.
Detectors have 100% relative efficiency, a typical
gamma-energy resolution of 2.8 keV for the 1332-keV
of (86+-4) % was placed upstream of the Ti sample.
The efficiencies of the detectors were determined using
a 152Eu point-like source and Monte Carlo simulations
to take into account the effect of the extended sample.
